		{
			description: ["Aquaculture 2 heavily expands fishing with 30+ catchable species organized by biome, a customizable rod system, and Neptune's Bounty treasure boxes fished from open ocean. The Iron Fishing Rod accepts hooks and fishing line as optional modifiers attached through the Tackle Box interface. Hooks change what fish can be caught; fishing line changes cast distance and retrieval speed. Build the full kit before heading to a dedicated fishing spot — the default vanilla rod cannot catch Aquaculture species."]
