			description: ["Pacific Halibut are a large flatfish caught in cold and frozen ocean biomes. Among the rarest of the standard ocean catches, the Pacific Halibut is identifiable by its flat body and spotted pattern. It provides high saturation when cooked and is a prestige catch in the Aquaculture 2 system."]
