		{
			description: ["Blobfish are found only in deep ocean biomes — specifically at significant depth. Alex's Mobs adds them as a passive deep-sea creature. Catching or killing a Blobfish requires going deep and searching carefully; they are ambient creatures that do not actively attack. Blobfish drop fish bones and are one of the more unusual aquatic collectable creatures in the pack."]
