			description: ["Blue Skies adds its own fish species to the Everbright and Everdawn dimensions — the Charscale Moki and Grittle Flatfish inhabit dimension-specific water sources. These are unique catches available only by fishing in their home dimension. Blue Skies fish do not drop in the overworld; access requires opening and stabilizing both Blue Skies portals first."]
