		{
			description: ["The Undergarden has its own aquatic ecology. The Gwibling is an Undergarden fish caught by fishing in the dimension's water sources. Raw Gwibling is edible but provides limited nutrition; cooked Gwibling provides significantly more. Undergarden fishing also levels the Mine and Slash Fishing profession and provides a source of Tiered Fish at appropriate levels when your character's fishing profession is leveled."]
