		{
			description: ["As the Mine and Slash Fishing profession levels, fishing yields Tiered Fish — Spiritual (1-20), Celestial (21-40), Empyrean (41-60), Angelic (61-80), Divine (81-100), and Godly (100). Tiered Fish are the primary ingredient in Mine and Slash Cooking recipes for seafood dishes that grant Experience and Loot bonuses when consumed. A dedicated fishing session with a high fishing level produces enough Tiered Fish for a full cooking batch."]
			id: "FI01000000000017"
