		{
			description: ["Neptune's Bounty is a special treasure chest item caught by fishing in open ocean biomes while using an Aquaculture 2 rod. Opening it has a chance to yield Neptunium Ingots — a rare material used to craft the Neptunium Fishing Rod and Neptunium armor. Neptunium Ingots cannot be crafted; they are exclusively obtained from Neptune's Bounty boxes. Dedicated ocean fishing is the only path to Neptunium."]
