		{
			dependencies: ["FI01000000000018"]
			description: ["The Neptunium Fishing Rod is the highest-tier fishing rod in Aquaculture 2, crafted from Neptunium Ingots obtained from Neptune's Bounty boxes. It has higher durability than the iron rod and improves the odds of catching rare fish and treasure boxes. The Neptunium Rod makes the Arapaima, Pacific Halibut, and rare dimension fish significantly more accessible — it is the endgame of the Aquaculture 2 system."]
