			description: ["The overworld's rivers and oceans, the Blue Skies dimensions, the Undergarden, and the deep ocean — each water source has its own fish population, its own catches, and its own ecological logic. The Master Angler has fished them all: rare freshwater giants, alien dimension fish, deep ocean creatures, and the Neptunium endgame. Fishing is not a passive activity in this pack. It is a fully realized profession with its own progression arc."]
